            <title><![CDATA[【深圳儿科医生的集体“狂飙”！《了不起的儿科医生》正式开机[666]】没错！最近你们的卫又搞了件大事情！重操摄影机对准了深圳儿科医生！由深圳卫健委、深圳儿...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【深圳儿科医生的集体“狂飙”！《了不起的儿科医生》正式开机<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[666]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6c/2022_666_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】没错！最近你们的卫又搞了件大事情！重操摄影机对准了深圳儿科医生！由深圳卫健委、深圳儿童医院发起，深圳广电、中广天择和bilibili共同打造的大型治愈系医疗纪实节目《了不起的儿科医生》正式开机！节目将镜头对准广东省唯一的儿童三甲医院——深圳市儿童医院，全天24小时全景式“无介入”拍摄，将儿童医院里最真实、最震撼的一面，原汁原味地呈现在观众面前，节目4月份上线！一整个狠狠期待住了哇～<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9Fyyds%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9Fyyds%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳医生yyds#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8D%AB%E5%81%A5%E5%A7%94%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8D%AB%E5%81%A5%E5%A7%94%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳卫健委了不起的儿科医生#</span></a> <a href="https://weibo.cn/sinaurl?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FOFrACCS9UxI5Gc2-u2_crQ" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbigunp4n4j216o0w0dne.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbiguw5liyj2154213hdt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbiguxoea2j2154213kjl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img styl